price: (30) On the Day We will say to Hell, "Have you been filled?" and it will say, "Are there some more,"
arabic: يَوۡمَ نَقُولُ لِجَهَنَّمَ هَلِ ٱمۡتَلَأۡتِ وَتَقُولُ هَلۡ مِن مَّزِيدٖ
